st: jubilate
st:lc: _Be Joyful_
l:b:O be joyful in the Lord, all you lands; *
l:b:i: serve the Lord with gladness,
l:b:i: and come before his presence with a song.
l:b:Be assured that the Lord, he is God; *
l:b:i: it is he that has made us, and not we ourselves;
l:b:i: we are his people, and the sheep of his pasture.
l:b:O go your way into his gates with thanksgiving,
l:b:and into his courts with praise; *
l:b:i: be thankful unto him, and speak good of his Name.
l:b:For the Lord is gracious, his mercy is everlasting, *
l:b:i: and his truth endures from generation to generation.
